data.description:
INSTANT EQUITY AND HUGE PRICE REDUCTION.  TOP NEIGHBORHOOD OF ARAPAHOE LAKE. Cherry Creek Schools. VERY Pretty House - VERY Traditional Floorplan. Smaller backyard mostly suited for patio entertaining and potted gardens.  New rock landscape, low maintenance. Overlooks one of the greenbelts of Arapahoe Lake.

Many improvements were made including new paint throughout, new carpet, new kitchen, new driveway, new hard surfaces, new light fixtures, new railings, refinished hard wood floors, updated baths and more. 

This is an opportunity not to be missed in Arapahoe Lake. The community is a "10" with location and amenities. Greenbelts, walkways, lakes, bridges, a competitive size swimming pool and tennis courts. 

Great Purchase Opportunity. Major Price Reduction.
